    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "I found the bug and it doesn't have anything to do with instant search ( I created a fork and updated your expo example, I can make a PR for it if I have time )\r\n\r\nThe issue is [react-native-gesture-handler](https://www.npmjs.com/package/react-native-gesture-handler), if you import it at the top of the project as react navigation recommend for [stack navigation](https://reactnavigation.org/docs/stack-navigator/#installation)  this bug will appear. I solved it by change from stack navigation to native stack navigation.",
